text: When you have a repo on GitHub, the API returns both "owner" and "organization" if the repo is from an organization. Can "owner" ever be different from "organization" when it is owner by an organization? <https://developer.github.com/v3/repos/#get>
The owner can be a user when a fork is from a private org
Which makes the fork still fall under the org's permissions
But the owner is the user
